{
  "stem": "1415.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember, during that time, we had to clean-- we had to clean and make sure there were no weeds next to the soccer fields.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember particularly having to clean that theater.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I-- I have a particular memory of given like a small bucket and something in my hand to wash that floor.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And-- and-- and me looking back, and that place looked so big, whether it was the stage, or the downstairs.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it looked like endless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the tears were just rolling down my eyes, with that little rag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I was afraid they're going to punish me if I don't get it done.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I remember, it-- it was very, very, very emotional, and I remember just-- stream-- my tears were just streaming down my face, and I was doing my work, and-- and I couldn't stop crying and looking back, and that place seemed to look bigger and bigger all the time.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was afraid I'll never get it done.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't remember whether I did or not.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I just remember that awful, terrible feeling and that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] helplessness, helplessness, sitting there on the floor on my knees, and-- and that vastness of that place when I looked back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It wasn't hard work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was just the overwhelming feeling of the vastness of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] This is mainly what we did in the camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And every once in a while, they would also take us to the factory to do some more loading of bricks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But mostly, we did take care of that Hitler-Jugend camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they were working.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were working.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were adults.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I assumed.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
